contents:
[[test]]
name = "integration"
required-features = [ "testing",]

[package]
authors = [ "Damir Jelić <poljar@termina.org.uk>",]
description = "A high level Matrix client-server library."
edition = "2021"
homepage = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-rust-sdk"
keywords = [ "matrix", "chat", "messaging", "ruma", "nio",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
name = "matrix-sdk"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-rust-sdk"
rust-version = "1.76"
version = "0.7.1"

[features]
default = [ "e2e-encryption", "automatic-room-key-forwarding", "sqlite", "native-tls",]
testing = [ "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/testing", "matrix-sdk-indexeddb?/testing", "matrix-sdk-base/testing", "wiremock", "matrix-sdk-test", "assert_matches2",]
e2e-encryption = [ "matrix-sdk-base/e2e-encryption", "matrix-sdk-base/message-ids", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/crypto-store", "matrix-sdk-indexeddb?/e2e-encryption",]
js = [ "matrix-sdk-common/js", "matrix-sdk-base/js",]
sqlite = [ "dep:matrix-sdk-sqlite", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/state-store",]
bundled-sqlite = [ "sqlite", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/bundled",]
indexeddb = [ "matrix-sdk-indexeddb/state-store",]
qrcode = [ "e2e-encryption", "matrix-sdk-base/qrcode",]
automatic-room-key-forwarding = [ "e2e-encryption", "matrix-sdk-base/automatic-room-key-forwarding",]
markdown = [ "ruma/markdown",]
native-tls = [ "reqwest/native-tls",]
rustls-tls = [ "reqwest/rustls-tls",]
socks = [ "reqwest/socks",]
sso-login = [ "dep:axum", "dep:rand", "dep:tower",]
image-proc = [ "dep:image",]
image-rayon = [ "image-proc", "image?/rayon",]
uniffi = [ "dep:uniffi", "matrix-sdk-base/uniffi",]
experimental-oidc = [ "ruma/unstable-msc2967", "ruma/unstable-msc4108", "dep:chrono", "dep:http_old", "dep:language-tags", "dep:mas-oidc-client", "dep:rand", "dep:sha2", "dep:tower", "dep:openidconnect",]
experimental-sliding-sync = [ "matrix-sdk-base/experimental-sliding-sync", "reqwest/gzip",]
experimental-widgets = [ "dep:language-tags", "dep:uuid",]
docsrs = [ "e2e-encryption", "sqlite", "indexeddb", "sso-login", "qrcode", "image-proc",]

[dependencies]
anymap2 = "0.13.0"
aquamarine = "0.5.0"
as_variant = "1.2.0"
async-channel = "2.2.1"
async-stream = "0.3.3"
async-trait = "0.1.60"
bytes = "1.1.0"
bytesize = "1.1"
event-listener = "5.3.0"
futures-core = "0.3.28"
http = "1.1.0"
indexmap = "2.0.2"
js_int = "0.2.2"
mime = "0.3.16"
mime2ext = "0.1.52"
serde = "1.0.151"
serde_html_form = "0.2.0"
serde_json = "1.0.91"
tempfile = "3.3.0"
thiserror = "1.0.38"
urlencoding = "2.1.3"
zeroize = "1.6.0"

[dev-dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.68"
assert-json-diff = "2"
assert_matches = "1.5.0"
assert_matches2 = "0.1.1"
dirs = "5.0.1"
futures-executor = "0.3.21"
once_cell = "1.16.0"
serde_urlencoded = "0.7.1"
similar-asserts = "1.5.0"
stream_assert = "0.1.1"

[dependencies.anyhow]
optional = true
version = "1.0.68"

[dependencies.assert_matches2]
optional = true
version = "0.1.1"

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.7.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.23"
optional = true

[dependencies.eyeball]
version = "0.8.7"
features = [ "tracing",]

[dependencies.eyeball-im]
version = "0.4.1"
features = [ "tracing",]

[dependencies.eyre]
version = "0.6.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3.26"
default-features = false
features = [ "alloc",]

[dependencies.http_old]
package = "http"
version = "0.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.imbl]
features = [ "serde",]
version = "2.0.0"

[dependencies.language-tags]
version = "0.3.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.mas-oidc-client]
version = "0.9.0"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-base]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-base"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-common]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-common"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-indexeddb]
optional = true
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-indexeddb"
version = "0.7.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-sqlite]
optional = true
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-sqlite"
version = "0.7.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-test]
optional = true
path = "testing/matrix-sdk-test"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.rand]
optional = true
version = "0.8.5"

[dependencies.ruma]
features = [ "rand", "unstable-msc2448", "unstable-msc2965", "unstable-msc3930", "unstable-msc3245-v1-compat", "unstable-msc2867", "client-api-c", "compat-upload-signatures", "compat-user-id", "compat-arbitrary-length-ids", "compat-tag-info", "compat-encrypted-stickers", "unstable-msc3401", "unstable-msc3266", "unstable-msc4075",]
git = "https://github.com/ruma/ruma"
rev = "e5a370f7e5fcebb0da6e4945e51c5fafba9aa5f0"

[dependencies.sha2]
optional = true
version = "0.10.8"

[dependencies.tokio-stream]
features = [ "sync",]
version = "0.1.14"

[dependencies.tower]
version = "0.4.13"
features = [ "make",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tracing]
features = [ "attributes", "std",]
version = "0.1.40"
default-features = false

[dependencies.uniffi]
optional = true
version = "0.27.1"

[dependencies.url]
features = [ "serde",]
version = "2.5.0"

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.4.1"
features = [ "serde", "v4",]
optional = true

[dependencies.vodozemac]
git = "https://github.com/matrix-org/vodozemac/"
rev = "4ef989c6a8eba0bc809e285a081c56320a9bbf1e"

[dependencies.image]
version = "0.25.1"
default-features = false
features = [ "default-formats",]
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.matrix-sdk-base]
features = [ "testing",]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-base"
version = "0.7.0"

[dev-dependencies.matrix-sdk-test]
path = "testing/matrix-sdk-test"
version = "0.7.0"

[dev-dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.11"
features = [ "env-filter",]

[lints.clippy]
assigning_clones = "allow"
box_default = "allow"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dev-dependencies]
wasm-bindgen-test = "0.3.33"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies]
tokio-util = "0.7.9"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies]
proptest = "1.4.0"
wiremock = "0.6.0"

[lints.rust.unexpected_cfgs]
level = "warn"
check-cfg = [ "cfg(tarpaulin_include)",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "docsrs",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.gloo-timers]
version = "0.3.0"
features = [ "futures",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12.4"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "macros", "sync",]
version = "1.30.0"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.backoff]
version = "0.4.0"
features = [ "tokio",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.openidconnect]
git = "https://github.com/poljar/openidconnect-rs"
rev = "c7e1dc31b83dd7559125984bfd36b9c0f191585e"
optional = true

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.reqwest]
features = [ "stream",]
version = "0.12.4"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "fs", "rt", "macros", "sync",]
version = "1.30.0"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.wiremock]
optional = true
version = "0.6.0"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "rt-multi-thread", "macros", "sync",]
version = "1.30.0"
default-features = false

[package]

name = "matrix-sdk-base"

stream_assert = "0.1.1"
web-time = "1.1.0"

[dependencies.assert_matches]

version = "1.5.0"

[dependencies.assert_matches2]

version = "0.1.1"

[dependencies.bitflags]

features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.eyeball]
version = "0.8.7"
features = [ "tracing",]

[dependencies.eyeball-im]
version = "0.4.1"
features = [ "tracing",]

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3.26"
default-features = false
features = [ "alloc",]

[dependencies.http]
optional = true
version = "1.1.0"

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-common]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-common"

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-crypto]

[dependencies.ruma]

[dependencies.tokio]

[dependencies.tracing]

[package]
